        <p>A pair of metal claws that are attached at the forearm, and extend outwards with sharp ends. Mantis Claws remained a popular addition to many rogue's arsenals for their dexterious and stylish design. </p>
        <p><b> Piercing Strike.</b></p>
        <p>The Mantis Claws extend out an additional 5ft as to reach an opponent,dealing an extra 1d8 piercing damage and, on a critical hit, will deal the bleeding effect. Will hit with disadvantage if the target is within 5ft of the user.</p>
        </description>
